detectors.description: Migration.tradeInTokens() (../../../Desktop/mainnet/00/005db38563B61fEed807b6dd131F41E736158959_Migration.sol#369-391) ignores return value by token2.transfer(msg.sender,amountToSend) (../../../Desktop/mainnet/00/005db38563B61fEed807b6dd131F41E736158959_Migration.sol#390)

Migration.tradeInTokens() (../../../Desktop/mainnet/00/005db38563B61fEed807b6dd131F41E736158959_Migration.sol#369-391) performs a multiplication on the result of a division:
	- amountToSend = token1Balance * tradingRatio (../../../Desktop/mainnet/00/005db38563B61fEed807b6dd131F41E736158959_Migration.sol#381)
	- tradingRatio = token1TotalSupply / token2TotalSupply (../../../Desktop/mainnet/00/005db38563B61fEed807b6dd131F41E736158959_Migration.sol#383)
